This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. Implements RFC 1950 (ZLIB Compressed Data Format Specification
version 3.3) directly, wrapping swift-deflate for the DEFLATE body.

The ADLER-32 reference implementation in `Decoder.adler32` follows
RFC 1950 § 9.

RFC 1950: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1950.html
